Link to home page David McCullough Interviewed June 15, 1989 David McCullough, author and historian, spoke to National Park Service employees about his research conducted in preparation for his book about Harry S Truman.
He addresses popular questions about Truman, Truman's childhood and developmental process; and Truman family relationships.
